  <title>Context</title>
  <shortdesc>
    <i>Context</i> (or 
	 <i>profile</i>) is an individual property of an individual visitor. It
	 contains information about the visitor, the current Location and Content. The
	 Context information that can be determined at a specific time is dependent on
	 the Channel. Aggregating Context information leads to Metrics or definition of
	 Audiences 
  </shortdesc>
